        %h2 Php-Server-Mon-Sys
        %p
          %strong Php-Server-Mon-Sys
          is a turnkey server monitor system, which installs an application named
          = succeed "." do
            %a{:href => "http://www.phpservermonitor.org/"} PHP Server Monitor v3.1.1
          , a basic yet very useful Open Source server monitor.  Php-Server-Mon-Sys installs not only PHP Server Monitor, but also the services it needs for operation; NGINX, MySQL, and PHP-FPM.  Because Php-Server-Mon-Sys uses Docker containers for deployment,  PHP-Server-Mon and its supporting services can be quickly and easily installed, managed, and uninstalled.
        %p
          For more information, read all about it on the
          = succeed "." do
            %a{:href => "https://github.com/addiscent/php-server-mon-sys"} Php-Server-Mon-Sys GitHub Repository
        %p
          Php-Server-Mon-Sys is Open Source,
          = succeed "." do
            %a{:href => "http://www.apache.org/licenses/"} Apache v2.0 license
        %br/
        %div.ss-box
          %p.aligncenter
            %h4
              View, download, or fork the "php-server-mon-sys" project on GitHub at:
              %br/
              %a{:href => "https://github.com/addiscent/php-server-mon-sys"} github.com/addiscent/php-server-mon-sys
          %p.aligncenter
            %big Screenshot
